                    <h1 class="fw-bold"><span id="typing-text"></span></h1>
                    <h1 class="fw-bold"><span id="typing-text"></span></h1>
                    <p class="lead mb-4 fw-bold">
                        Book your Dream car anytime, anywhere with just a few clicks!
                    </p>

